This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning (RL) and reward design, which are core topics in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which encompasses a broad range of topics related to the design and analysis of algorithms that can learn from data. Additionally, the paper also touches upon topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), control engineering (cs.CE), and systems and control (cs.SY), as it discusses the application of RL in critical care settings. These sub-categories are also likely because they are closely related to the core topics of the paper and are often studied in conjunction with RL.
